NB: in case the best 'interior' team in the Segunda División would have
    finished 6th, 7th, 8th or 9th, Bella Vista (Paysandú) would have been
    entitles to a play-off against them, but meanwhile it is mathematically
    certain that the best 'interior' team will finish 5th or better.

